title: Fibonacci Sequence
description:
Implement a function `fibonacci(n)` that returns the nth Fibonacci number. The sequence starts with F(0)=0, F(1)=1, and each subsequent number is the sum of the two preceding ones.

Examples:
- fibonacci(0) = 0
- fibonacci(1) = 1
- fibonacci(5) = 5
- fibonacci(10) = 55
